798
00:47:52,753 --> 00:47:54,250
<b>I think you have a call.</b>

799
00:47:54,255 --> 00:47:56,215
<b>Oh, excuse me.</b>

800
00:47:58,192 --> 00:48:01,225
<b>It's my sister. I'll be back.</b>

801
00:48:04,832 --> 00:48:07,865
<b>She's so cheerful.</b>

802
00:48:07,935 --> 00:48:11,195
<b>I bet she makes everyone around her laugh a lot.</b>

803
00:48:11,372 --> 00:48:13,870
<b>I haven't seen you laugh this much in a long time.</b>

804
00:48:13,874 --> 00:48:15,640
<b>Really?</b>

