811
00:48:36,830 --> 00:48:38,425
<b>Later.</b>

812
00:48:38,666 --> 00:48:40,895
<b>I'll tell you everything later.</b>

813
00:48:41,235 --> 00:48:45,495
<b>I've always kept my word.</b>

814
00:48:46,640 --> 00:48:48,265
<b>I promise...</b>

