00:48:50,744 --> 00:48:52,335
<b>Really.</b>

817
00:48:56,116 --> 00:48:57,975
<b>Okay. Let's eat.</b>

818
00:49:00,821 --> 00:49:04,790
<b>Gosh, it's been a while since I had steak.</b>

819
00:49:04,792 --> 00:49:07,325
<b>Wait. I'll cut it for you.</b>

820
00:49:08,262 --> 00:49:11,355
<b>Yes. I'm having a meal with Anchor Lee and his mother.</b>

821
00:49:11,999 --> 00:49:14,625
<b>No, it's not uncomfortable at all.</b>

822
00:49:14,668 --> 00:49:17,065
<b>She's really nice.</b>

823
00:49:17,538 --> 00:49:20,340
<b>Okay. I'll be back soon.</b>

824
00:49:20,341 --> 00:49:22,070
<b>Okay. I got it.</b>

825
00:49:22,076 --> 00:49:23,635
<b>Okay.</b>

