00:49:30,317 --> 00:49:32,045
<b>Here you go.</b>

827
00:49:38,859 --> 00:49:40,990
<b>I had such a nice meal thanks to you.</b>

828
00:49:40,995 --> 00:49:43,190
<b>Please let me treat you to a meal next time.</b>

829
00:49:43,197 --> 00:49:44,590
<b>Will you?</b>

