<b>Don't get the wrong idea. It didn't mean anything.</b>

920
00:56:31,238 --> 00:56:33,170
<b>I hope you're not upset.</b>

921
00:56:33,173 --> 00:56:34,700
<b>I won't get the wrong idea.</b>

922
00:56:34,708 --> 00:56:36,505
<b>And I'm not upset either.</b>

923
00:56:37,577 --> 00:56:40,445
<b>I'm just uncomfortable about this kind of situation.</b>

924
00:56:40,847 --> 00:56:42,740
<b>I hate that you're walking on eggshells around me...</b>

925
00:56:42,749 --> 00:56:44,915
<b>because of my condition.</b>

926
00:56:46,253 --> 00:56:48,515
<b>I've had this condition for a long time.</b>

927
00:56:48,688 --> 00:56:51,055
<b>And I'm used to this.</b>

928
00:56:51,491 --> 00:56:53,955
<b>So you don't need to try hard for my sake.</b>

929
00:56:54,761 --> 00:56:56,955
<b>I wasn't trying hard.</b>

930
00:56:58,498 --> 00:57:01,595
<b>To be honest, when I found out about your condition,</b>

931
00:57:02,035 --> 00:57:05,795
<b>I just thought that I got to know you a bit more.</b>

932
00:57:06,072 --> 00:57:08,835
<b>That's not true. It got harder.</b>

933
00:57:09,643 --> 00:57:11,570
<b>I studied and kept thinking about it,</b>

934
00:57:11,578 --> 00:57:14,305
<b>but I still don't know...</b>

935
00:57:15,015 --> 00:57:19,045
<b>how it must feel to live with all the memories one has.</b>

936
00:57:22,022 --> 00:57:24,715
<b>On one side, I'm jealous.</b>

937
00:57:25,525 --> 00:57:27,555
<b>And on the other side, I feel bad.</b>

938
00:57:30,464 --> 00:57:33,830
<b>I'm sorry. I won't write notes if this upsets you.</b>

939
00:57:33,834 --> 00:57:36,225
<b>But please don't misunderstand my intention.</b>

940
00:57:36,336 --> 00:57:39,535
<b>I'm doing this for me, not for you.</b>

941
00:57:41,374 --> 00:57:43,405
<b>I can forget about other things,</b>

942
00:57:44,211 --> 00:57:48,075
<b>but I really want to remember everything about you.</b>

943
00:57:49,349 --> 00:57:52,045
<b>I don't want to forget anything when it comes to you.</b>

944
00:58:30,323 --> 00:58:33,015
<b>Why isn't he answering his phone?</b>

945
00:58:37,163 --> 00:58:39,295
<b>Why are you still here?</b>

946
00:58:39,332 --> 00:58:41,330
<b>Chul was supposed to come, but he's not coming.</b>

947
00:58:41,334 --> 00:58:43,295
<b>And he's not answering either.</b>

948
00:58:43,603 --> 00:58:44,600
<b>What about your sister?</b>

949
00:58:44,604 --> 00:58:47,840
<b>She left earlier because she had an important meeting.</b>

950
00:58:47,841 --> 00:58:50,265
<b>That's why Chul was supposed to come.</b>

951
00:58:51,311 --> 00:58:53,505
<b>Chul must be here.</b>

952
00:58:53,947 --> 00:58:55,575
<b>Hey, Chul.</b>

953
00:58:56,683 --> 00:58:59,675
<b>What? Why can't you come? Where are you?</b>

954
00:59:00,921 --> 00:59:03,445
<b>Okay. I understand.</b>

955
00:59:03,890 --> 00:59:05,885
<b>No, I'll manage.</b>

956
00:59:06,293 --> 00:59:07,855
<b>Okay.</b>

957
00:59:10,130 --> 00:59:11,830
<b>Hop in. I'll give you a ride.</b>

958
00:59:11,831 --> 00:59:13,700
<b>It's okay. I'll take a taxi.</b>

959
00:59:13,700 --> 00:59:16,965
<b>My friend got hospitalized, so I have to go to the hospital.</b>

960
00:59:17,404 --> 00:59:18,965
<b>Get in.</b>

961
00:59:24,544 --> 00:59:25,540
<b>Thank you.</b>

962
00:59:25,545 --> 00:59:28,080
<b>I'm sorry you had to do this instead of going home.</b>

963
00:59:28,081 --> 00:59:29,805
<b>It's okay.</b>

964
00:59:29,983 --> 00:59:33,515
<b>Does he break his promise very often? Your manager, I mean.</b>

965
00:59:33,687 --> 00:59:36,120
<b>Oh, we told him before to take today off,</b>

966
00:59:36,122 --> 00:59:38,490
<b>so I guess he was hanging out somewhere far away.</b>

967
00:59:38,491 --> 00:59:41,025
<b>He's usually not like that. He's very diligent.</b>

968
00:59:41,595 --> 00:59:42,990
<b>Really?</b>

969
00:59:42,996 --> 00:59:44,555
<b>Right.</b>

970
00:59:45,031 --> 00:59:48,265
<b>Ta-da. I bought this. Your mother's poetry book.</b>

971
00:59:49,769 --> 00:59:51,600
<b>That was published a while ago. How did you find it?</b>

972
00:59:51,605 --> 00:59:54,735
<b>I got curious and looked for it right away as soon as I met her.</b>

973
00:59:54,741 --> 00:59:57,110
<b>I don't know much about poetry, but I loved it.</b>

974
00:59:57,110 --> 00:59:58,840
<b>I instantly became her fan.</b>

975
00:59:58,845 --> 01:00:02,305
<b>If I get to meet her again, I'll ask her for an autograph.</b>

976
01:00:03,183 --> 01:00:04,780
<b>She'll be thrilled.</b>

977
01:00:04,784 --> 01:00:07,150
<b>She looks a lot like you.</b>

978
01:00:07,153 --> 01:00:09,085
<b>Especially the way you smile.</b>

979
01:00:09,756 --> 01:00:13,055
<b>I'm sure you only have good memories of her.</b>

980
01:00:14,828 --> 01:00:16,425
<b>You're right.</b>

981
01:00:16,963 --> 01:00:18,925
<b>She always...</b>

982
01:00:19,032 --> 01:00:22,225
<b>gave me nothing but good memories since when I was a kid.</b>

983
01:00:24,304 --> 01:00:27,405
<b>(Soojeong University Hospital)</b>

984
01:00:28,441 --> 01:00:31,310
<b>Thank you for the ride. Go home safely.</b>

985
01:00:31,311 --> 01:00:33,005
<b>Will you be all right by yourself?</b>

986
01:00:33,513 --> 01:00:35,675
<b>There are a lot of people.</b>

987
01:00:42,088 --> 01:00:43,745
<b>What's wrong?</b>

988
01:00:47,360 --> 01:00:49,725
<b>(Father)</b>

989
01:00:59,739 --> 01:01:01,365
<b>Anchor Lee.</b>

990
01:01:59,466 --> 01:02:02,325
<b>(We thank Shin Dong Mi, Kim Nam Hui for their guest appearance.)</b>

991
01:02:16,049 --> 01:02:18,550
<b>(Find Me in Your Memory)</b>

992
01:02:18,551 --> 01:02:19,810
<b>Can you fix my disease?</b>

993
01:02:19,819 --> 01:02:23,590
<b>Anchor Lee, time can't help you.</b>

994
01:02:23,590 --> 01:02:25,450
<b>Just keep your eyes on him.</b>

995
01:02:25,458 --> 01:02:26,490
<b>Keep my eyes on him?</b>

996
01:02:26,493 --> 01:02:28,460
<b>I can't let Jeong Hoon get destroyed.</b>

997
01:02:28,461 --> 01:02:30,860
<b>What on earth happened to Mom?</b>

998
01:02:30,864 --> 01:02:32,660
<b>She wanted this.</b>

999
01:02:32,665 --> 01:02:34,160
<b>She felt too bad for you.</b>

1000
01:02:34,167 --> 01:02:36,830
<b>She did this out of love.</b>

1001
01:02:36,836 --> 01:02:40,770
<b>I'm so happy that you're with me, Jeong Hoon.</b>

1002
01:02:40,774 --> 01:02:42,840
<b>Are you sure that you were happy?</b>

1003
01:02:42,842 --> 01:02:46,275
<b>It's okay, Jeong Hoon. It'll be fine.</b>

